    "Note that Previous work focused on in-DPU performance, without evaluating the cost of these individuia operations.",
    "As noted in prior research [24], and demonstrated in our results, these operations can significantly affect UPMEM's overall performance.Fig. 9 shows the total execution time of vPIM (with all optimizations enabled) for different configurations.",
    "The configuration in Fig. 9.a involves 60 DPUs and a 60MB input file size for each DPU.",
    "We vary the number of vCPUs.",
    "In Fig. 9.b, we vary the number of DPUs while maintaining a constant input file size of 60MB for each DPU and 16 vCPUs."
